        <rdfs:comment>In order to assign a role to an actor, this reification class was introduced.Through the property hadParticipant an event is related with this class.ActorWithRole is related with the class Actor through the property hasSubjectand to a literal that represents the role through the property hasRole.</rdfs:comment>
    </Class>
    


