        <ontology:hasDescription>The MOVING reference member state of this VC (Value Chain) is SWITZERLAND 2. The reference MOVING Card ID of this VC is VC 11 CH2. The cake is produced and sold directly by about fifteen bakers in the canton or in small local shops.  </ontology:hasDescription>
